William J. BRENNAN, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
BERGEN COUNTY PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE, Frank Puccio, Custodian of Records for the Bergen County Prosecutor's Office, Defendants. M-1485 September Term 2017
078074 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs is remanded to the trial court for disposition. Jurisdiction is not retained.
